actionConfiguration.body:
select
        m.app_id,
        a.name as appName,
        t.name as WorkspaceName,
        count(*) as message_count
from
     public.messages m
join 
    public.apps a
on
   m.app_id = a.id
join 
    public.tenants t 
on
        a.tenant_id = t.id
where
        m.created_at>'{{SelectDate.selectedOptionValue || utils.getLastDaysRange(7)}}'
group by
        t.name,
        m.app_id,
        a.name
order by
        message_count desc
limit 20;
